Title: 2. Stakeholders
Write-Up Text: People are excitedly discussing the recently announced Australian budget. In a social media post the author shared a lively picture with @joshburnsmp in Brighton talking about how the new budget will benefit all Aussies. It's great to see top shots discussing such critical topics and propelling positive change. #BudgetAnnouncement #BrightonTalks #AussiePride.
